<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.8">
<l>ampa ramaṉal kālni lañcala māki niṉṟava mararkōṉ</l>
<l>vampu lāmalar mēlma limaṭa maṅkai taṉkoḻu naṉavaṉ</l>
<l>kompi ṉaṉṉavi ṭaima ṭakkuṟa mātar nīḷita ṇantoṟum</l>
<l>cempu ṉamavai kāval koḷtiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam where ruddy fields</l>
<l>Have simple Kuṟava ladies, with twig-like waists,</l>
<l rend="indent">[on] every high platform as guards,</l>
<l>[The place] of him who is the husband of the happy, simple lady</l>
<l rend="indent">on the blossom where fragrance wafts,</l>
<l>The king of celestials who endures as the firmament, fire, wind, earth, and water.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
